@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jmpbul(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.58
    tmp = v2
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.66 * tmp + 0.98) / 0.28) / wp.abs(v2))
    v0 = ((v1 / v2) + (wp.exp(v2 + 0.26) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.03)))
    data[tid] = v0
